706
01:08:47,907 --> 01:08:49,374
For the first time.

707
01:08:50,209 --> 01:08:51,506
I'm so scared.

708
01:08:54,613 --> 01:08:57,446
But the thing is, I like it. I want more.

709
01:09:01,353 --> 01:09:02,342
Look.

710
01:09:04,790 --> 01:09:08,282
You're married to the first man
in the history of the world...

711
01:09:08,561 --> 01:09:10,586
